00:07:44.650 --> 00:07:47.350
specified in a digital form.

00:07:47.350 --> 00:07:48.680
I'm going to say four things.

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:53.640
It's just a set of
promises in a digital form.

00:07:53.640 --> 00:07:57.070
So it's not handwritten out.

00:07:57.070 --> 00:07:58.330
It includes protocols.

00:07:58.330 --> 00:07:59.825
