just-- kind of a root.

00:09:02.650 --> 00:09:06.490
Now, I would also say, however,
that smart contracts may not

00:09:06.490 --> 00:09:07.657
be so smart.

00:09:07.657 --> 00:09:09.490
A lot of people have
come to be calling them

00:09:09.490 --> 00:09:11.950
dumb contracts that
are just algorithms

00:09:11.950 --> 00:09:14.170
that perform a function.

00:09:14.170 --> 00:09:17.920
So don't think of them as
artificial intelligence.

00:09:17.920 --> 00:09:23.710
That's another class provided
next semester by Simon Johnson.

00:09:23.710 --> 00:09:28.900
Think of them almost
as just dumb contracts.

00:09:28.900 --> 00:09:31.050
And in a sense,
they're mechanizing

00:09:31.050 --> 00:09:35.280
what might otherwise be done
amongst and between humans.

00:09:35.280 --> 00:09:38.280
And smart contracts may or
may not be really contracts.

00:09:38.280 --> 00:09:40.210
