00:22:54.490 --> 00:22:56.080
this semester about
market values,

00:22:56.080 --> 00:22:57.538
I thought it would
give you a sense

00:22:57.538 --> 00:22:58.870
of how people think about it.

00:22:58.870 --> 00:23:02.240
The other five that you
did some reading about.

00:23:02.240 --> 00:23:05.260
EOS, whose market value
is about $5 billion,

00:23:05.260 --> 00:23:09.070
is so new, because they just
finished an initial coin

00:23:09.070 --> 00:23:10.900
offering in July.

