00:28:17.470 --> 00:28:22.290
But the tokens are usually
issued before they're usable.

00:28:22.290 --> 00:28:24.430
And a token is some
native currency

00:28:24.430 --> 00:28:27.620
to be used on a network.

00:28:27.620 --> 00:28:32.160
The development is open
but highly centralized.

00:28:32.160 --> 00:28:35.310
The promoters usually
give themselves some skin

00:28:35.310 --> 00:28:38.130
